      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a functional, budget-friendly option for daily transportation. While the engine and transmission are operational and the car drives fine, there are visible signs of age including some exterior paint fading and minor interior wear. It has been maintained decently over the years, though a buyer should expect some upcoming routine service requirements typical for a car of this age. It's a solid, honest vehicle for someone looking for utility over aesthetics.",
