    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, and the care shows in every detail. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, chips, or dings, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather seats are firm and free of any wear or creasing, and the interior is entirely smoke-free, retaining that fresh new-car scent. Every electronic feature, from the high-definition navigation system to the premium surround-sound audio, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete, documented service history from the original dealership and a recent multi-point inspection that returned a perfect bill of health. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a collector-quality vehicle in peak condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
